h4.MapTransferSoftCapFix (int) - (AccessLevel 9) [Notes|Command_MapTransferSoftCapFix_GameServerLib]
__CATEGORY MISC setting
If true (the default) allow a map transfer to a partition that is over the softCap when a non-team-transfer has a team member on the destination map
Theoretically we can remove this after it's been on live for a bit. WOLF[6May2013]
